  {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "Wproposeaert flowacontinuum of sparse regressionmodels jointly forallregularization parameters $\\lambda$ andall $l _ { q }$ norms,icdingooesub $\\mathbf { \\cdot } l _ { 1 }$ pseudo-norms. ",
